snippet.title: Amber Heard Becomes Highest Paid Actor Because Of Cancelling Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
When it comes to Hollywood and acting in general, there is a certain "goal" if you will that many men and women in the business try to achieve. Mainly...they want to make a lot of money. Yes, it's true that many times the "better roles" is the more immediate goal in some of their eyes, but in truth, if they get paid well enough, they couldn't care less about the roles. Plus, the more money they're making, the more they "prove" how good they are as many are willing to pay them that amount. Which brings us to Amber Heard, whom is being surrounded by rumors about her own salary for an upcoming film. We'll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC76r9K-_Knc7d38c9uKRwaw?sub_confirmation=1 

And there you have it, everyone! A look at Amber Heard and whether the rumors about her "pay increase" are warranted or just the latest in a long line of potential things that may never happen. Do you think Amber Heard is worth a lot of money in regards to her acting? Or should she get less money because of what she's done to Johnny Depp?
